### ============================================================
### ROLES — Quản lý role & gán permission vào role (yêu cầu ROLE_ADMIN)
### ============================================================

### [1] Lấy danh sách tất cả roles (kèm permissions)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### [2] Tạo role ROLE_MANAGER
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "ROLE_MANAGER"
}

### [3] Tạo role ROLE_VIEWER
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "ROLE_VIEWER"
}

### [4] Gán nhiều permissions vào role
# Thay {{roleId}} bằng id role, điền permissionIds từ kết quả GET /admin/permissions
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/roles/{{roleId}}/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "permissionIds": [
    "permissionId1",
    "permissionId2"
  ]
}

### [5] Gỡ một permission khỏi role
# Thay {{roleId}} và {{permissionId}} bằng id thực tế
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/roles/{{roleId}}/permissions/{{permissionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### [6] Xóa role theo ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/roles/{{roleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
